powerpc/vdso: Refactor 32 bits and 64 bits pages setup

The setup of VDSO pages is identical for 32 bits VDSO and
64 bits VDSO.

Refactor that setup.

And use &vdsoXX_start which is synonym of vdsoXX_kbase.

